<paragraph blockId="37.[160,1155,454,584]" box="[160,409,454,480]" pageId="37" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,409,454,480]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="302">External morphology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[160,1155,454,584]" pageId="37" pageNumber="302">Shell external, patelliform, covering entire body; protoconch on the posterior part, farther from the head; with white longitudinal lines, background red. Body background beige to white with concentrations of red marks in the front.</paragraph>
